WEBVTT

00:02.863 --> 00:04.802
Hey, so I saw a movie trailer
the other day.

00:04.855 --> 00:07.213
How could Batman
possibly fight Superman?

00:07.214 --> 00:08.746
I mean, isn't that dumb?

00:08.748 --> 00:10.048
Maybe he uses Kryptonite.

00:10.050 --> 00:12.050
Well, Batman's got
a lot of money.

00:12.052 --> 00:15.019
Maybe he builds a suit that can
do everything Superman can do.

00:15.021 --> 00:16.354
No, no, no, no, no.

00:16.356 --> 00:18.289
I've seen that movie.
It's called <i> Iron Man.</i>

00:25.732 --> 00:27.866
(quietly):
What is happening?

00:27.868 --> 00:30.368
I don't know.

00:30.370 --> 00:32.871
But it's beautiful.

00:34.407 --> 00:35.974
And now Ben Affleck
is Batman?

00:35.976 --> 00:38.176
Oh, he was great in
<i>Shakespeare in Love.</i>

00:38.178 --> 00:40.178
Ooh, we should watch that
next girls' night.

00:40.180 --> 00:41.379
We could do a double feature

00:41.381 --> 00:42.947
with the Leonardo DiCaprio
<i>Romeo + Juliet.</i>

00:42.949 --> 00:44.716
Oh, I love me some Leo.

00:44.718 --> 00:46.384
And it's gone.

00:47.454 --> 00:49.320
Oh, hello, everyone.

00:49.322 --> 00:52.257
I am happy to report
I'm feeling much better.

00:52.259 --> 00:53.658
Good for you.

00:53.660 --> 00:54.859
(muttering)

00:54.861 --> 00:57.662
My fever is gone,
my sinuses are pressure-free,

00:57.664 --> 01:01.165
and my mucus is as clear
as a Yosemite waterfall.

01:02.569 --> 01:04.669
Glad to hear it.

01:05.839 --> 01:08.540
I'll be able to return
to work tomorrow.

01:09.509 --> 01:11.943
Yay.

01:11.945 --> 01:14.412
Well, why isn't
everyone happy?

01:14.414 --> 01:18.149
Your little ray of sunshine
is ready to beam again.

01:18.985 --> 01:21.052
You really don't know why?
No.

01:21.054 --> 01:23.988
But I knew that his “yay”
was sarcastic.

01:23.990 --> 01:26.090
Not bad for a guy
whose last bowel movement

01:26.092 --> 01:28.259
sounded like rain on a roof.

01:30.297 --> 01:32.931
Let me refresh your memory.

01:33.833 --> 01:34.966
Penny,

01:34.968 --> 01:37.802
rub Vicks on my chest.

01:37.804 --> 01:40.605
Sheldon, I cooked you breakfast.

01:40.607 --> 01:42.040
I made your bed.

01:42.042 --> 01:43.942
I checked your mouth for thrush.

01:44.811 --> 01:46.878
You can rub your own chest.

01:46.880 --> 01:49.480
Oh, sure, grope every other
male on the planet,

01:49.482 --> 01:51.082
but draw the line with me.

01:52.886 --> 01:55.420
I brought you a little
care package from work.

01:55.422 --> 01:56.621
It's our latest
antiviral

01:56.623 --> 01:58.590
and the best decongestant
we make.

01:58.592 --> 02:01.292
I hope laughter
is the best medicine,

02:01.294 --> 02:04.128
'cause this care package
is a joke.

02:04.965 --> 02:06.965
Hey, she came
all the way here...

02:06.967 --> 02:08.532
(sneezes)

02:12.505 --> 02:15.273
You're gonna want
to take these with food.

02:16.977 --> 02:19.577
Sheldon,
stop being a baby

02:19.579 --> 02:21.579
and let Emily
take a look at you.

02:21.581 --> 02:23.615
SHELDON: She's a
dermatologist.

02:23.617 --> 02:25.583
I went to medical school.

02:25.585 --> 02:27.485
Well, in that case,
try removing

02:27.487 --> 02:29.320
the irritating
patch of brown skin

02:29.322 --> 02:31.022
standing next to you.

02:33.727 --> 02:37.028
All right, here you go.

02:37.030 --> 02:39.163
Leonard, I'm dying.

02:39.165 --> 02:41.666
You're not dying.
It's just the flu.

02:41.668 --> 02:43.001
I asked for chicken noodle.

02:43.003 --> 02:46.104
This is chicken and stars.
It's killing me.

02:49.342 --> 02:52.010
I never did get
that chicken noodle, did I?

02:53.079 --> 02:56.648
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

02:56.650 --> 02:59.984
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

02:59.986 --> 03:01.619
♪ The Earth began to cool ♪

03:01.621 --> 03:04.155
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

03:04.157 --> 03:06.824
♪ We built the Wall ♪
♪<i> We built the pyramids</i> ♪

03:06.826 --> 03:09.494
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

03:09.496 --> 03:11.396
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

03:11.398 --> 03:13.364
♪<i> Bang!</i> ♪

03:13.367 --> 03:17.367
